adafruit-nrfutil is a Python package that includes the adafruit-nrfutil
command line utility and the nordicsemi library.

This package is derived from the Nordic Semiconductor ASA package
pc-nrfutil, version 0.5.3. The code has been converted from Python 2 to
Python 3.

The executable nrfutil has been renamed to adafruit-nrfutil to
distinguish it from the original executable.

This tool can be used with the Adafruit nRF52 Feather to flash firmware
images onto the device using the simple serial port.
